(3073, 'Bases Matemáticas: Álgebra', 'EdX keeps courses open for enrollment after they end to allow learners to explore content and continue learning.', 'EdX keeps courses open for enrollment after they end to allow learners to explore content and continue learning. All features and materials may not be all available. Check back often to see when new course start dates are announced.  En este curso se recordará lo que es una ecuación  con una única incógnita y cómo solucionarla. A partir de ahí se tratarán: ', 'https://edx.org/course/bases-matematicas-algebra-upvalenciax-bma101x', 'http://www.youtube.com/v/pxy2QPrV8YM?version=3&amp;autohide=1', '2015-11-24', 28, 'https://www.edx.org/sites/default/files/styles/course_video_banner/public/course/image/featured-card/bases-matematicas-algebra_378x225.jpg?itok=VddJbLsg', 'Math', 'edX', 0, 'Español', 'yes', 'UPValenciaX', '2015-11-24 23:09:30'),
(3074, 'Basic Mandarin Chinese – Level 1', 'Introductory Mandarin is the first in a series of six courses designed to teach you how to speak Mandarin Chinese.', 'Introductory Mandarin is the first in a series of six courses designed to teach you how to speak Mandarin Chinese. This course will introduce you to the basic language you will need to eat, live, and get around in Mandarin speaking countries. Since this is a language course, we recommend taking this course with a friend or group of friends. Practicing with others by speaking the language will help you learn it more effectively. Additionally, Mandarin is a tonal language, which means that in order to truly master it, you will need to say the words out loud! Join the community of over 900 million native Mandarin speakers and start learning today!  ', 'https://edx.org/course/basic-mandarin-chinese-level-1-mandarinx-mx101x', 'http://www.youtube.com/v/nS_k1h7JRLs?version=3&amp;autohide=1', '2015-11-24', 42, 'https://www.edx.org/sites/default/files/styles/course_video_banner/public/course/image/featured-card/mx101z-378x225.png?itok=cBf52nAT', 'Language', 'edX', 0, 'English', 'yes', 'MandarinX', '2015-11-24 23:09:30'),
