(5147, 'Основы микроэкономики Microeconomics Principles', 'Самое сложное экономическое событие сводится, в конечном счёте, к действиям отдельных людей и фирм. Микроэкономика показывает, как можно эти действия анализировать – как люди выбирают, что потреблять, а фирмы – что производить.\nMicroeconomic theory tells how people decide what to consume, and firms – what to produce and how to win over their competitors in the market.\n', 'Самое сложное экономическое событие сводится, в конечном счёте, к действиям отдельных людей и фирм. Микроэкономика показывает, как можно эти действия анализировать – как люди выбирают, что потреблять, а фирмы – что производить.\nMicroeconomic theory tells how people decide what to consume, and firms – what to produce and how to win over their competitors in the market.\n', 'https://class.coursera.org/microeconomic-001/', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4tHmha8ITSE', '2014-04-07', 10, 'https://coursera-course-photos.s3.amazonaws.com/84/96a4bb6789f3fcceb8217ccca28ba2/microeconom.jpg', 'Economics & Finance,', 'Coursera', 0, 'Russian', 'no', 'Higher School of Economics,', '2015-11-18 00:00:00'),
(5148, 'Основы корпоративных финансов Fundamentals of Corporate Finance', 'Мы рассмотрим принципы и модели финансового анализа компании, а также оценку стратегических решений компании с точки зрения их влияния на фундаментальную стоимость компании.\nIn this course you will learn the principles and models of financial analysis of a firm based on the criteria of value creation.\n', 'Мы рассмотрим принципы и модели финансового анализа компании, а также оценку стратегических решений компании с точки зрения их влияния на фундаментальную стоимость компании.\nIn this course you will learn the principles and models of financial analysis of a firm based on the criteria of value creation.\n', 'https://class.coursera.org/corpfin-001/', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zfEy1b-JLbw', '2014-06-30', 11, 'https://coursera-course-photos.s3.amazonaws.com/8e/babc3621cec2144897866dcda42389/Corporate-finance.jpg', 'Economics & Finance,', 'Coursera', 0, 'Russian', 'no', 'Higher School of Economics,', '2015-11-18 00:00:00'),
(5149, 'Core Concepts in Data Analysis', 'Learn both theory and application for basic methods that have been invented either for developing new concepts – principal components or clusters, or for finding interesting correlations – regression and classification.   This is preceded by a thorough analysis of 1D and 2D data.', 'Learn both theory and application for basic methods that have been invented either for developing new concepts – principal components or clusters, or for finding interesting correlations – regression and classification.   This is preceded by a thorough analysis of 1D and 2D data.', 'https://class.coursera.org/datan-001/', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=f7_Tcgih-Mw', '2014-04-21', 8, 'https://coursera-course-photos.s3.amazonaws.com/a0/74fb126920e6979ff4cbbe26e41797/core-in-data.jpg', 'Statistics and Data Analysis,', 'Coursera', 0, 'English', 'no', 'Higher School of Economics,', '2015-11-18 00:00:00'),
(5151, 'Макроэкономика Macroeconomics', 'Курс посвящен изучению макроэкономических вопросов, таких как долгосрочный рост, циклические колебания экономики и стабилизационная политика государства.\n\nThe course covers major macroeconomic issues, such as long-run growth, cyclical fluctuations of the economy, and stabilization policy. ', 'Курс посвящен изучению макроэкономических вопросов, таких как долгосрочный рост, циклические колебания экономики и стабилизационная политика государства.\n\nThe course covers major macroeconomic issues, such as long-run growth, cyclical fluctuations of the economy, and stabilization policy. ', 'https://class.coursera.org/macroec-002/', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_cG2AKUnw1U', '2015-11-18', 10, 'https://coursera-course-photos.s3.amazonaws.com/6a/a7f4946004bdf4a99193647b5061ff/macroeconomics-_3_.jpg', 'Economics & Finance,', 'Coursera', 0, 'Russian', 'no', 'Higher School of Economics,', '2015-11-18 00:00:00'),
(5153, 'Unethical Decision Making in Organizations', 'This course Unethical decision making in organizations : A seminar on the dark side of the force will teach you how strong organizational contexts push good people towards unethical decisions. You will also learn how to protect yourself and your organization against such forces lurking in the dark.', 'This course Unethical decision making in organizations : A seminar on the dark side of the force will teach you how strong organizational contexts push good people towards unethical decisions. You will also learn how to protect yourself and your organization against such forces lurking in the dark.', 'https://class.coursera.org/unethicaldecision-002/', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4d7f6cb0248e11e4b83cd5b84ff19601', '2015-09-15', 7, 'https://coursera-course-photos.s3.amazonaws.com/ff/079482ccced35e86a8a9ea70e0c0e4/Biz_ethics_Fotolia_49499572.png', 'Humanities ,Business & Management,Social Sciences,', 'Coursera', 0, 'English', 'no', 'University of Lausanne,', '2015-11-18 00:00:00'),
(5154, 'Analyzing Global Trends for Business and Society', 'What does the future hold for global markets? How are societies and cultures evolving? Who will be global powers of the 21st century? Take this class and find out how global trends are transforming business and society.', 'What does the future hold for global markets? How are societies and cultures evolving? Who will be global powers of the 21st century? Take this class and find out how global trends are transforming business and society.', 'https://class.coursera.org/globaltrends-003/', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dac1afe0c69911e49d11571b3a3104c4', '2015-05-04', 7, 'https://coursera-course-photos.s3.amazonaws.com/2e/be8bd086e111e3815a9df972b8069e/MauroLogo.jpg', 'Economics & Finance,Business & Management,Social Sciences,', 'Coursera', 0, 'English', 'no', 'University of Pennsylvania,', '2015-11-18 00:00:00'),
(5156, 'Введение в биоинформатику Introduction to Bioinformatics', 'Курс «Введение в биоинформатику» адресован тем, кто хочет получить расширенное представление о том, что такое биоинформатика и как она помогает биологам и медикам в их работе.\n\n\nThe course is aimed at those who would like to have a better idea of what bioinformatics is and how it helps biologists and medical scientists in research and clinical work. ', 'Курс «Введение в биоинформатику» адресован тем, кто хочет получить расширенное представление о том, что такое биоинформатика и как она помогает биологам и медикам в их работе.\n\n\nThe course is aimed at those who would like to have a better idea of what bioinformatics is and how it helps biologists and medical scientists in research and clinical work. ', 'https://class.coursera.org/bioinfo-002/', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=98c3e6305dd511e4a24d07c8fbea2b2c', '2015-10-20', 6, 'https://d15cw65ipctsrr.cloudfront.net/21/afb410501011e583f2f15e93198f03/______________.png', 'Computer Science: Theory,Information, Tech & Design,Health & Society,Biology & Life Sciences,', 'Coursera', 0, 'Russian', 'no', 'Saint Petersburg State University,', '2015-11-18 00:00:00'),
(5157, 'Philosophy and the Sciences', 'Learn about the historical and philosophical foundations of contemporary science. \nExplore cutting-edge debates in the philosophy of the physical sciences and philosophy of the cognitive sciences.', 'Learn about the historical and philosophical foundations of contemporary science. \nExplore cutting-edge debates in the philosophy of the physical sciences and philosophy of the cognitive sciences.', 'https://class.coursera.org/philsci-002/', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bSteXM0hTiE', '2015-09-21', 8, 'https://coursera-course-photos.s3.amazonaws.com/cf/0e6f355ee930b55faf574d1d89a990/iStock_000018892265XSmall.jpeg', 'Humanities ,Physical & Earth Sciences,Computer Science: Artificial Intelligence,Physics,', 'Coursera', 0, 'English', 'no', 'The University of Edinburgh,', '2015-11-18 00:00:00'),
(5158, 'Animal Behaviour and Welfare', 'Animal welfare has been described as a complex, multi-faceted public policy issue which includes important scientific, ethical, and other dimensions. Improving our understanding of  animal welfare, involves the fascinating study of animal behavior as well as the challenge of accessing the emotions of animals. This is the second time we have run this course, and we have revised some of the content and assessments in line with the great feedback we gained from our first run through. We have also added some subtitles to the videos for the Spanish and Mandarin speakers who wish to participate. Talk about this course using the hashtag #EdAniWelf', 'Animal welfare has been described as a complex, multi-faceted public policy issue which includes important scientific, ethical, and other dimensions. Improving our understanding of  animal welfare, involves the fascinating study of animal behavior as well as the challenge of accessing the emotions of animals. This is the second time we have run this course, and we have revised some of the content and assessments in line with the great feedback we gained from our first run through. We have also added some subtitles to the videos for the Spanish and Mandarin speakers who wish to participate. Talk about this course using the hashtag #EdAniWelf', 'https://class.coursera.org/animal-002/', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=23w01CdK9Bs', '2015-02-09', 6, 'https://coursera-course-photos.s3.amazonaws.com/e0/b9a9af76525b66801e0e89826b8414/ABW-Dog.jpg.jpeg', 'Health & Society,Biology & Life Sciences,Social Sciences,', 'Coursera', 0, 'English', 'no', 'The University of Edinburgh,', '2015-11-18 00:00:00'),
(5160, 'Understanding Violence', 'Violence is among the top three leading causes of injury and death in the US and globally.  We will focus on different disciplinary approaches and perspectives to understanding and potentially preventing violence.', 'Violence is among the top three leading causes of injury and death in the US and globally.  We will focus on different disciplinary approaches and perspectives to understanding and potentially preventing violence.', 'https://class.coursera.org/violence-001/', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5f4942e011bf11e492cabb1075344783', '2014-09-03', 6, 'https://coursera-course-photos.s3.amazonaws.com/01/336f608f5f11e3a9f91bb3aff3b3bb/violence_chalkboard.png', 'Humanities ,Health & Society,Social Sciences,', 'Coursera', 0, 'English', 'no', 'Emory University,', '2015-11-18 00:00:00'),
(5161, 'Fundamentals of Music Theory', 'This course will introduce students to the theory of music, providing them with the skills needed to read and write Western music notation, as well as to understand, analyse, and listen informedly. It will cover material such as pitches and scales, intervals, clefs, rhythm, form, meter, phrases and cadences, and basic harmony. ', 'This course will introduce students to the theory of music, providing them with the skills needed to read and write Western music notation, as well as to understand, analyse, and listen informedly. It will cover material such as pitches and scales, intervals, clefs, rhythm, form, meter, phrases and cadences, and basic harmony. ', 'https://class.coursera.org/musictheory-002/', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7hF-fT733Vs', '2015-08-03', 5, 'https://coursera-course-photos.s3.amazonaws.com/3c/bae235189d7b003920f00383916814/logo.jpg', 'Music, Film, and Audio,', 'Coursera', 0, 'English', 'no', 'The University of Edinburgh,', '2015-11-18 00:00:00'),
(5162, 'Sports and Building Aerodynamics', 'Have we reached the boundaries of what can be achieved in sports and building design? The answer is definitely “NO”. This course explains basic aspects of bluff body aerodynamics, wind tunnel testing and Computational Fluid Dynamics CFD simulations with application to sports and building aerodynamics. It is intended for anyone with a strong interest in these topics. Key fields addressed are urban physics, wind engineering and sports engineering. ', 'Have we reached the boundaries of what can be achieved in sports and building design? The answer is definitely “NO”. This course explains basic aspects of bluff body aerodynamics, wind tunnel testing and Computational Fluid Dynamics CFD simulations with application to sports and building aerodynamics. It is intended for anyone with a strong interest in these topics. Key fields addressed are urban physics, wind engineering and sports engineering. ', 'https://class.coursera.org/spobuildaerodynamics-002/', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TbaKkVY43Dg', '2015-11-09', 6, 'https://coursera-course-photos.s3.amazonaws.com/13/0c7d2e5ac13e3a0241d6ca00b56597/thumbnail.jpg', 'Information, Tech & Design,Engineering,Physics,', 'Coursera', 0, 'English', 'no', 'Eindhoven University of Technology,', '2015-11-18 00:00:00'),
(5164, 'Learning to Teach Online', 'Based upon the award winning* educational resources of same name developed by Simon McIntyre and Karin Watson, the Learning to Teach Online LTTO MOOC is designed to help existing educators establish or improve their own online or blended teaching practices. The target audience is primarily teachers in higher education, K-12, community college, and vocational or private education.', 'Based upon the award winning* educational resources of same name developed by Simon McIntyre and Karin Watson, the Learning to Teach Online LTTO MOOC is designed to help existing educators establish or improve their own online or blended teaching practices. The target audience is primarily teachers in higher education, K-12, community college, and vocational or private education.', 'https://class.coursera.org/ltto-003/', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=746ae250f2e211e49e1229d7f14d3aeb', '2015-11-18', 6, 'https://coursera-course-photos.s3.amazonaws.com/23/0ef590c44411e3aad2734e308cbf7c/Unknown-1.jpeg', 'Education,Teacher Professional Development,', 'Coursera', 0, 'English', 'no', 'UNSW Australia (The University of New South Wales),', '2015-11-18 00:00:00'),
(5165, 'Durabilité : état des lieux planétaire, scénarios envisageables', 'Ce cours propose de dresser en premier lieu un état de la planète en termes de répartition de la richesse sur terre et de problèmes environnementaux globaux. A partir de là denvisager les scénarios possibles et dapprofondir la notion de durabilité.', 'Ce cours propose de dresser en premier lieu un état de la planète en termes de répartition de la richesse sur terre et de problèmes environnementaux globaux. A partir de là denvisager les scénarios possibles et dapprofondir la notion de durabilité.', 'https://class.coursera.org/durabilite-001/', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=', '2015-11-18', 5, 'https://coursera-course-photos.s3.amazonaws.com/e9/452cd94349c0bf177c4ab65212a860/Durabilite_Fotolia_42512989_web_600x340.png', 'Humanities ,Social Sciences,', 'Coursera', 0, 'French', 'no', 'University of Lausanne,', '2015-11-18 00:00:00'),
(5166, 'The Clinical Psychology of Children and Young People', 'The course will cover the basic guiding principles of the Clinical Psychology of Children and Young People and illustrate how theories of psychological development can be applied in understanding children and young peoples mental health and well being within a wider societal and cultural context. We will also discuss current psychological models of prevention and treatment for Children and Young People.', 'The course will cover the basic guiding principles of the Clinical Psychology of Children and Young People and illustrate how theories of psychological development can be applied in understanding children and young peoples mental health and well being within a wider societal and cultural context. We will also discuss current psychological models of prevention and treatment for Children and Young People.', 'https://class.coursera.org/clinicalpsych-002/', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3669cba0d5ca11e3961df1a63fae85ed', '2015-05-18', 6, 'https://coursera-course-photos.s3.amazonaws.com/39/af5235253127cecd6b8db826d1dc00/4269396864_d6efda2bb8_o.jpg', 'Medicine,Health & Society,Biology & Life Sciences,Social Sciences,Teacher Professional Development,', 'Coursera', 0, 'English', 'no', 'The University of Edinburgh,', '2015-11-18 00:00:00'),
(5168, 'An Introduction to Consumer Neuroscience & Neuromarketing ', 'This course will introduce you to the multidisciplinary field of consumer neuroscience and neuromarketing. It will go through to the basic concepts of the human brain, the elements of the consumer mind, how it is studied, and how its insights can be applied in commercial and societal understandings of consumer behaviour.', 'This course will introduce you to the multidisciplinary field of consumer neuroscience and neuromarketing. It will go through to the basic concepts of the human brain, the elements of the consumer mind, how it is studied, and how its insights can be applied in commercial and societal understandings of consumer behaviour.', 'https://class.coursera.org/neuromarketing-001/', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=811d8b504a0011e4900e93bf72a8ec54', '2014-11-10', 6, 'https://coursera-course-photos.s3.amazonaws.com/6e/f6800d9aa59cab44a6b239a6d8c62e/banner1__1280x720px.png', 'Computer Science: Theory,Economics & Finance,Medicine,Humanities ,Biology & Life Sciences,', 'Coursera', 0, 'English', 'no', 'Copenhagen Business School,', '2015-11-18 00:00:00'),
(5170, '法与社会   Law and Society', '       “法与社会”这门课程要在多层多样的社会关系中解读法律，并且透过法律来考察和把握社会的各种现象。本课程将课堂讲授与媒体教学有机结合，使学生对法社会学有一概括了解，用比较的眼光对法律制度和规范的内容进行分析，对中国法律传统及其演变进行准确定位。\n\n\n       "Law and Society" aims to offer both readings of law that vary with the diversity of social relations and understandings of social events from the legal perspective. This module, through a combination of lectures with multimedia presentation, is designed to enable the students to gain a general knowledge of sociology, to analyse legal institutions and norms by comparative means, and to have a clearer idea of the legal tradition and its evolution in China.      ', '       “法与社会”这门课程要在多层多样的社会关系中解读法律，并且透过法律来考察和把握社会的各种现象。本课程将课堂讲授与媒体教学有机结合，使学生对法社会学有一概括了解，用比较的眼光对法律制度和规范的内容进行分析，对中国法律传统及其演变进行准确定位。\n\n\n       "Law and Society" aims to offer both readings of law that vary with the diversity of social relations and understandings of social events from the legal perspective. This module, through a combination of lectures with multimedia presentation, is designed to enable the students to gain a general knowledge of sociology, to analyse legal institutions and norms by comparative means, and to have a clearer idea of the legal tradition and its evolution in China.      ', 'https://class.coursera.org/sjtula014-001/', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4XdF49_BoF4', '2014-01-01', 11, 'https://coursera-course-photos.s3.amazonaws.com/78/f4d5696a89a8fb803583e03ffa2c55/____2.jpg', 'Law,', 'Coursera', 0, 'Chinese', 'no', 'Shanghai Jiao Tong University,', '2015-11-18 00:00:00'),
(5171, '数学之旅 The Journey of Mathematics', '课程从问题开始揭示一些数学思想形成的过程，和听众一起从思想上重走一遍前辈们走过的路，体会数学抽象的魅力。\n\nIn this course I share the processes which formed the core concepts of mathematical philosophy, walking with students as they experience, learn and enjoy mathematical abstraction.', '课程从问题开始揭示一些数学思想形成的过程，和听众一起从思想上重走一遍前辈们走过的路，体会数学抽象的魅力。\n\nIn this course I share the processes which formed the core concepts of mathematical philosophy, walking with students as they experience, learn and enjoy mathematical abstraction.', 'https://class.coursera.org/sjtuma153-001/', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yK3jYuHEFKo', '2013-12-01', 6, 'https://coursera-course-photos.s3.amazonaws.com/9a/a2c5d35bec672ccb155d455374e78f/____.jpg', 'Mathematics,', 'Coursera', 0, 'Chinese', 'no', 'Shanghai Jiao Tong University,', '2015-11-18 00:00:00'),
(5174, 'Теория отраслевых рынков Industrial Organization', 'Курс посвящен закономерностям конкуренции, рассматриваемой в рамках концепции стратегического взаимодействия продавцов, включая олигополистическую конкуренцию и решения укоренившегося продавца, сталкивающегося с опасностью входа.\nExplore the factors that determine firm size and market structures by analyzing the strategic decisions made by market participants.', 'Курс посвящен закономерностям конкуренции, рассматриваемой в рамках концепции стратегического взаимодействия продавцов, включая олигополистическую конкуренцию и решения укоренившегося продавца, сталкивающегося с опасностью входа.\nExplore the factors that determine firm size and market structures by analyzing the strategic decisions made by market participants.', 'https://class.coursera.org/industorg-001/', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9XhZHuA4E9Q', '2014-04-07', 9, 'https://coursera-course-photos.s3.amazonaws.com/94/fdab4411cb6ff3fd4d651a71c5d635/industrial.jpg', 'Economics & Finance,', 'Coursera', 0, 'Russian', 'no', 'Higher School of Economics,', '2015-11-18 00:00:00');
