(5175, 'Approche pluridisciplinaire du dopage', 'Lobjectif du cours est de permettre une compréhension pluridisciplinaire du dopage. Ce cours est une opportunité dobserver comment diverses disciplines abordent un même objet, selon différents angles et de manière complémentaire. Il sagit également de donner des repères permettant dappréhender le dopage dans sa complexité.', 'Lobjectif du cours est de permettre une compréhension pluridisciplinaire du dopage. Ce cours est une opportunité dobserver comment diverses disciplines abordent un même objet, selon différents angles et de manière complémentaire. Il sagit également de donner des repères permettant dappréhender le dopage dans sa complexité.', 'https://class.coursera.org/dopage-001/', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=', '2015-11-18', 5, 'https://coursera-course-photos.s3.amazonaws.com/71/84cd0f76019b5d5e67f1b96d1d4f1b/Dopage_Fotolia_48342765_web_600x340.png', 'Health & Society,Social Sciences,', 'Coursera', 0, 'French', 'no', 'University of Lausanne,', '2015-11-18 00:00:00'),
(5177, 'Emergence of Life', 'How did life emerge on Earth? How have life and Earth co-evolved through geological time? Is life elsewhere in the universe? Take a look through the 4-billion-year history of life on Earth through the lens of the modern Tree of Life!', 'How did life emerge on Earth? How have life and Earth co-evolved through geological time? Is life elsewhere in the universe? Take a look through the 4-billion-year history of life on Earth through the lens of the modern Tree of Life!', 'https://class.coursera.org/emergenceoflife-002/', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=296565e0273111e599394fb44654ae20', '2014-10-20', 8, 'https://coursera-course-photos.s3.amazonaws.com/13/40d710904011e3bde831dfcc35571d/ESE111-Logo-02.jpg', 'Physical & Earth Sciences,Biology & Life Sciences,', 'Coursera', 0, 'English', 'no', 'University of Illinois at Urbana-Champaign,', '2015-11-18 00:00:00'),
(5178, 'Sustainable Food Production Through Livestock Health Management', 'Learn about the impact of infectious disease on sustainable animal-based food production by understanding the science of growth, immunity, and infection and by learning the problem-solving skills needed to advance animal health and food production through optimal management practices.', 'Learn about the impact of infectious disease on sustainable animal-based food production by understanding the science of growth, immunity, and infection and by learning the problem-solving skills needed to advance animal health and food production through optimal management practices.', 'https://class.coursera.org/sustainablefood-001/', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1c761c1053c611e49e7ea521c58e6bb8', '2015-01-26', 6, 'https://coursera-course-photos.s3.amazonaws.com/26/1392c18d81c21f84f37c4de112e785/food-sustainability-logo.jpg', 'Economics & Finance,Medicine,Health & Society,Biology & Life Sciences,Business & Management,Food and Nutrition,', 'Coursera', 0, 'English', 'no', 'University of Illinois at Urbana-Champaign,', '2015-11-18 00:00:00'),
(5180, 'Childbirth: A Global Perspective', 'This course will review challenges for maternal and newborn health in the developing world, where a great many women and babies are suffering from complications during pregnancy, childbirth, and the days following birth. Themes covered include the epidemiology of maternal and newborn mortality and morbidity, relevant issues for the global health workforce, community-based interventions to improve maternal and newborn health and survival, and sociocultural dynamics surrounding birth.', 'This course will review challenges for maternal and newborn health in the developing world, where a great many women and babies are suffering from complications during pregnancy, childbirth, and the days following birth. Themes covered include the epidemiology of maternal and newborn mortality and morbidity, relevant issues for the global health workforce, community-based interventions to improve maternal and newborn health and survival, and sociocultural dynamics surrounding birth.', 'https://class.coursera.org/pregnancychildbirth-001/', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3bab945023e911e4b0734d3332ba0f76', '2014-10-01', 6, 'https://coursera-course-photos.s3.amazonaws.com/d8/6708ed8a79e722dce3585c152e6df3/pregnancy1.png', 'Humanities ,Health & Society,Biology & Life Sciences,Social Sciences,', 'Coursera', 0, 'English', 'no', 'Emory University,', '2015-11-18 00:00:00'),
(5181, 'The Art and Archaeology of Ancient Nubia', 'This course examines the development of the art and architecture of the cultures of ancient Nubia through what we have learned from archaeology and how that evidence has helped us create the picture we now have of the culture and history of the birth and development of art and civilization in the Nile Valley. ', 'This course examines the development of the art and architecture of the cultures of ancient Nubia through what we have learned from archaeology and how that evidence has helped us create the picture we now have of the culture and history of the birth and development of art and civilization in the Nile Valley. ', 'https://class.coursera.org/ancientnubia-001/', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=u2r-cdD4QTo', '2014-04-30', 8, 'https://coursera-course-photos.s3.amazonaws.com/ae/78e16a017786f4c9c898e460bd4986/nubia2.png', 'Humanities ,Social Sciences,Arts,', 'Coursera', 0, 'English', 'no', 'Emory University,', '2015-11-18 00:00:00'),
(5182, 'The Bibles Prehistory, Purpose, and Political Future', 'How and why was the Bible written? Drawing on the latest archeological research and a wide range of comparative texts, this course synthesizes fascinating recent research in biblical studies and presents a powerful new thesis: Facing catastrophic defeat, the biblical authors created a new form of community—what today we would call "peoplehood." Their achievements bear directly on modern questions of politics, economics, and theology.', 'How and why was the Bible written? Drawing on the latest archeological research and a wide range of comparative texts, this course synthesizes fascinating recent research in biblical studies and presents a powerful new thesis: Facing catastrophic defeat, the biblical authors created a new form of community—what today we would call "peoplehood." Their achievements bear directly on modern questions of politics, economics, and theology.', 'https://class.coursera.org/biblefuture-001/', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1ntJ-wF2pE8', '2014-05-26', 6, 'https://coursera-course-photos.s3.amazonaws.com/51/b1c0ccbfc15fb49e3719618b36929f/wright-class.jpg', 'Humanities ,Social Sciences,', 'Coursera', 0, 'English', 'no', 'Emory University,', '2015-11-18 00:00:00'),
(5185, 'Экономика труда Labor economics', 'В курсе изучаются основы экономической теории рынка труда, объясняющие поведение основных участников рынка труда – домохозяйств, фирм и государства. \nWe will study the economic theory of the labor market, explaining the behavior of the main agents in the labor market - households, firms and the state.\n', 'В курсе изучаются основы экономической теории рынка труда, объясняющие поведение основных участников рынка труда – домохозяйств, фирм и государства. \nWe will study the economic theory of the labor market, explaining the behavior of the main agents in the labor market - households, firms and the state.\n', 'https://class.coursera.org/laborec-001/', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aruFkXQo-7g', '2015-11-18', 10, 'https://coursera-course-photos.s3.amazonaws.com/8f/0c68a19de9ed55e258ad8bfbcd1804/econtruda-_1_.jpg', 'Economics & Finance,', 'Coursera', 0, 'Russian', 'no', 'Higher School of Economics,', '2015-11-18 00:00:00'),
(5186, 'История экономической мысли History of Economic Thought', 'Курс поможет осмыслить извечные проблемы жизни человека: богатство и бедность, деньги и рынки, инфляция и безработица, индивидуальные решения и государственная политика.\nThe course will help you to understand the lasting economic problems of everyday human life: wealth and poverty, money and markets, inflation and unemployment, human decisions and governmental policies. ', 'Курс поможет осмыслить извечные проблемы жизни человека: богатство и бедность, деньги и рынки, инфляция и безработица, индивидуальные решения и государственная политика.\nThe course will help you to understand the lasting economic problems of everyday human life: wealth and poverty, money and markets, inflation and unemployment, human decisions and governmental policies. ', 'https://class.coursera.org/historyofec-001/', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5MOVLJsTuzQ', '2014-04-04', 11, 'https://coursera-course-photos.s3.amazonaws.com/55/b1254d747896918be6b9ae8a34e622/History-of-Economics.jpg', 'Economics & Finance,', 'Coursera', 0, 'Russian', 'no', 'Higher School of Economics,', '2015-11-18 00:00:00'),
(5187, '粒子世界探秘 Exploring Particle World', '本课程以通俗的语言介绍粒子物理的主要内容和最前沿的研究。课程涉及的主要内容包括： 物质和反物质， 夸克和强相互作用，中微子和弱相互作用，对称性和它的作用， 粒子物理的标准模型，粒子天文学， 暗物质。\n\nThis course gives an brief introduction of the main content and the frontier of particle physics in popular language. It includes: matter and antimatter, quark and strong interaction, neutrino and weak interaction, symmetry and its applications, standard model of particle physics, particle astronomy, dark matter etc.\n\n', '本课程以通俗的语言介绍粒子物理的主要内容和最前沿的研究。课程涉及的主要内容包括： 物质和反物质， 夸克和强相互作用，中微子和弱相互作用，对称性和它的作用， 粒子物理的标准模型，粒子天文学， 暗物质。\n\nThis course gives an brief introduction of the main content and the frontier of particle physics in popular language. It includes: matter and antimatter, quark and strong interaction, neutrino and weak interaction, symmetry and its applications, standard model of particle physics, particle astronomy, dark matter etc.\n\n', 'https://class.coursera.org/sjtujxdepw-001/', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cfOzt86GMc8', '2014-01-01', 10, 'https://coursera-course-photos.s3.amazonaws.com/98/fca76c19d91f3d0bf41e929bf8755a/keji_GALAXY.JPG', 'Physical & Earth Sciences,Physics,', 'Coursera', 0, 'Chinese', 'no', 'Shanghai Jiao Tong University,', '2015-11-18 00:00:00'),
