(6186, 'Sexing the Canvas: Art and Gender', 'What do paintings tell us about sex? How is art gendered? Here we get up close to some of the great paintings in the world’s most famous museums, giving you insight into how art speaks to us about sex, sexuality and gender.', 'What do paintings tell us about sex? How is art gendered? Here we get up close to some of the great paintings in the world’s most famous museums, giving you insight into how art speaks to us about sex, sexuality and gender.', 'https://class.coursera.org/sexingthecanvas-001/', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=d5ca1170470011e5ae5f49a234d265da', '2015-10-26', 7, 'https://d15cw65ipctsrr.cloudfront.net/09/26dbd079c411e4805cfbc6f353669c/The_Dream_by_Rousseau.jpg', 'Humanities ,Arts,', 'Coursera', 0, 'English', 'no', 'The University of Melbourne,', '2015-11-18 00:00:00'),
(6187, 'Rethinking Ageing:  Are we prepared to live longer?', 'Population ageing is occurring in nearly every country around the word. This MOOC takes a multidisciplinary approach to explore the impact of living longer and takes into account the technological advancements, the built environment, economics and ethics to rethink what it means to age well now and in the future.', 'Population ageing is occurring in nearly every country around the word. This MOOC takes a multidisciplinary approach to explore the impact of living longer and takes into account the technological advancements, the built environment, economics and ethics to rethink what it means to age well now and in the future.', 'https://class.coursera.org/ageing-001/', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0c85d360c09311e495558ba01ce8979a', '2015-03-23', 7, 'https://d15cw65ipctsrr.cloudfront.net/d9/5c3b10a5ed11e4a1c005d94e4ea434/ageing_02-_2_.jpg', 'Economics & Finance,Information, Tech & Design,Health & Society,Social Sciences,', 'Coursera', 0, 'English', 'no', 'The University of Melbourne,', '2015-11-18 00:00:00'),
