(6820, 'Algorithms for DNA Sequencing', 'We will learn computational methods -- algorithms and data structures -- for analyzing DNA sequencing data. We will learn a little about DNA, genomics, and how DNA sequencing is used.  We will use Python to implement key algorithms and data structures and to analyze real genomes and DNA sequencing datasets.\n', 'We will learn computational methods -- algorithms and data structures -- for analyzing DNA sequencing data. We will learn a little about DNA, genomics, and how DNA sequencing is used.  We will use Python to implement key algorithms and data structures and to analyze real genomes and DNA sequencing datasets.\n', 'https://class.coursera.org/ads1-007/', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8eb1b4f0d6d011e4ac4bf1c0de0fc3c6', '2015-12-07', 4, 'https://d15cw65ipctsrr.cloudfront.net/0c/727630056211e587470dc112902bf4/genomics_algorithms.jpg', 'Computer Science: Theory,Biology & Life Sciences,Computer Science: Software Engineering,', 'Coursera', 0, 'English', 'no', 'Johns Hopkins University,', '2015-11-18 00:00:00'),
